  <name>MS TODO App</name>
  <summary>Microsoft TODO management application for the COSMIC desktop</summary>
  <description>
    <p>A Microsoft TODO management application for the COSMIC™ desktop, forked from the original Tasks app by Eduardo Flores</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Exceptional performance and responsiveness.</li>
        <li>Effortless keyboard shortcut support.</li>
        <li>Expressive emoji integration.</li>
        <li>Microsoft TODO integration.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Original Developer:</strong> Eduardo Flores (edfloreshz@proton.me)</p>
    <p><strong>Fork Maintainer:</strong> digit1024</p>
  </description>
  <branding>
    <color type="primary" scheme_preference="light">#eaeaff</color>
    <color type="primary" scheme_preference="dark">#280c4b</color>
  </branding>
  <icon type="remote" height="256" width="256">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/digit1024/msToDO/master/res/icons/hicolor/scalable/apps/com.github.digit1024.MS_TODO_APP.svg</icon>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">com.github.digit1024.MS_TODO_APP.desktop</launchable>
  <releases>
    <release version="0.2.0" date="2025-01-27">
        <description>
            <p>Forked and rebranded as MS TODO App! 🚀</p>
            <ul>
                <li>✨ <em>Rebranded as MS TODO App</em></li>
                <li>🔗 <em>Updated to new repository</em></li>
                <li>☕ <em>Added Buy Me a Coffee support</em></li>
                <li>🎯 <em>Microsoft TODO integration focus</em></li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.2.0" date="2025-05-27">
        <description>
            <p>Powerful new features! 🚀</p>
            <ul>
                <li>✨ <em>Sub-tasks support</em></li>
                <li>🔍 <em>Search functionality</em></li>
                <li>📊 <em>Task sorting</em></li>
                <li>🎨 <em>Expanded icon library</em></li>
                <li>🌍 <em>Enhanced internationalization</em></li>
                <li>🔧 <em>Better task management</em></li>
                <li>⌨️ <em>Improved keyboard shortcuts</em></li>
                <li>🎯 <em>Hide completed tasks</em></li>
                <li>📋 <em>Enhanced export options</em></li>
                <li>🐛 <em>Bug fixes and performance improvements</em></li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.1.1" date="2024-11-06">
        <description>
            <p>Text editor for notes 🎉</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Notes now has a multiline text editor</li>
                <li>The window has a border</li>
                <li>The theme is now synced with COSMIC</li>
                <li>The about page has been revamped</li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.1.0" date="2024-07-02">
        <description>
            <p>Initial release! 🎉</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Organize tasks into lists</li>
                <li>Rest your eyes with dark mode</li>
                <li>Manage tasks with ease using keyboard shortcuts</li>
                <li>Export tasks to Markdown</li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
  </releases>
